      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like there is nothing left. i used to see the world in colors and shapes, like every shadow had a purpose. now it's just... gray. i sit in front of the canvas and it's like looking into a black hole. it's not just that i can't paint, it's like the part of me that actually *was* someone is just gone. i'm just walking around in this skin, but the person inside is empty. just a hollow shell.",
